Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.41,0:02:02.31,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Dreamless dorm, ticking clock
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:07.12,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I walk away from the soundless room
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:12.10,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Windless night, moonlight melts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:17.11,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}My ghostly shadow to the lukewarm gloom
