Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:24.44,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}of bleeding sword
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:29.36,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Reminds me that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:34.21,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I still live
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:43.34,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I will burn my dread
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:46.06,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I once ran away from the god of fear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:48.76,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}And he chained me to despair, oh yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:53.35,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Burn my dread
