Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.79,0:00:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Social Links you've cultivated have unlocked new powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Temperance, the Tower, Death, the Devil, and the Hermit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you've obtained so many at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.76,0:00:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already made an impressive number of Social Links.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you converse and develop a deeper understanding with others,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your bonds will strengthen and facilitate another change in your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer vacation's really over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.31,0:00:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got lost on the way to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}was{\i0} a pretty long break.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but c'mon, getting lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.18,0:00:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you even realized you got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:00:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.46,0:01:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're— Wait, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the "Little Detective."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shirogane.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.94,0:01:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't call me by any other weird names you've thought up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.18,0:01:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt that greetings were somewhat in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police investigation may be over,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.04,0:01:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there are still several points that leave me unconvinced.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I have some family issues,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.64,0:01:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll be staying here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be a freshman here starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try to get along, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{OP dialogue in between. have fun with that.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been dying to go on this school trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll hit up all the tourist spots!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:56.55,Yellow Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(144,192)\frz349.992\blur1}Enjoy checking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:56.55,Yellow Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(132,261)\frz349.992\blur1}out the sights
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take pictures with the girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:58.18,Yellow Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\pos(1262,119)\frz344.549\blur0.6\xshad5\yshad8\c&H07E5F2&}Make fun memories with
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:58.18,Yellow Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\pos(1243,186)\frz344.549\blur0.6\xshad5\yshad8\c&H07E5F2&}the girls
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:02:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe have a romantic encounter in an unfamiliar town!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Day 1: Cultural exchange."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Day 2: View factories and such during our free time."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.34,0:02:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Day 3: Go home."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with the cultural exchange crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{}It's like a social studies trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want rural and suburban students to interact, so we'll be visiting a private school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't we get any free time?{yosuke background}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This trip's itinerary was supposedly created by King Moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Is our free time {\i1}really{\i0}  free time?!{yosuke background}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is King Moron tormenting us from beyond the grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.49,0:02:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freshmen and sophomores get to go together starting this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the decline in students,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they decided to save money by holding the trip every other year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I doubt we'll get bored with you guys around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Tatsumi Port Island like?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a large city on an artificial island facing the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:03:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, could we invite Naoto whenever we go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little worried about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't he come here specifically to help out with that case?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He may be a detective, but he's just a normal kid once the case is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, he's a fellow transfer student, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Well, uh, next, I will explain about our educational institution and the reasons for its establishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This school's way too big!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uh, I'd like to start with a proverb— Er, I can't waste too much of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like three Juneses combined.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}As such, I shall hereby draw this assembly to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narukami, this is a school, not Junes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was that funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, everyone, to Gekkoukan High School!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honor to meet you all today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:04:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the student council president, Fushimi Chihiro from Class 3-B.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HHHNNNGGG!{you guys are such faggots}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! She's the most bewitching bespectacled beauty I've ever beheld!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those glasses {\i1}are{\i0} pretty hip{ster}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the one showing you around campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be my honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time our school has invited another student body for a true cultural exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do our best to ensure a worthwhile experience for each and every one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, your group is going to have a special lecture in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, uh, does everyone know about the gods who made our country?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The two gods who made our country were the god Izanagi and the goddess Izanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want him to finish up so we can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have lectures all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The two got along really well until one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were great in class today, kiddos!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading over to our lodgings for the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all that today, I'm hoping tonight's rooming is something else!
