Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All righty, here we are. The Seaside Clamshell Inn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be staying here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just opened not too long ago, and the price was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't just stand there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those in front, get a move on! Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really a normal hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just screams sketchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have these modern hotels in Inaba, so I can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... This area is called "Shirakawa Boulevard," and it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They probably refurbished a place that had gone under, and, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's a love—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That's far enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't sound weird when Narukami says it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's okay.{in bed}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives? You always go easy on him.{in bed}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faster than I expected.{in bed}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they were to meet me... I wonder, what the look on Yosuke's face would be like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's that voice coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoo-bee doo-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teddie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bear the loneliness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew where you were going thanks to Yosuke's "Trip Guide."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, when did you see that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you get here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took the train like a normal bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swore off Topsicles and saved up the money I got working at Junes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to take an unbearably slow train here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teddie, you've been through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why'd you come dressed like that? You look like a freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I almost got thrown in the trash a couple times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I kept hanging onto the promise Yukiko made to go on a date with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, let's all go out during our free time tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bear-rilliant idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoo-bee doo-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the record, I'm cool with sharing a room with you girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beat!{bears, beets, battlestar galactica}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here. Isn't this bed awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waterbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really bouncy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting too hyped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Switch on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it!{so this is what girls do at sleepovers}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're spinning! I'm gonna get dizzy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is kinda unnerving, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to stand there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why don't we test out the bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude! Don't invite me to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha— Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.31,0:08:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep telling you I don't swing that way, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way to know for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoo-bee! Shoo-bee doo-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, don't you trust me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pissing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax! Relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for, punk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Those are some suspicious-looking buttons!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bam! Bam! Bam! Bam! Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo! This is great!{wah? what are we gonna do on the bed?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this soothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I can't sleep here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm gonna sleep here with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,School trips are supposed to be more...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're fucking sleeping outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But I already took my bath and don't have a change of clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a pic for posterity?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare!
