Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:56.20,Default lessborders,,0000,0000,0000,,Teddie, how about we go in that building?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:57.89,Default lessborders,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
