Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where are Teddie and the girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we lost them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks. Let's split up and look for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you ashamed of yourself for ganging up on him?!
