Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! You can hit my face, my gut, or wherever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you better leave this kid alone!
