Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness they're leaving you alone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
