Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you calmed down a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm sorry I made you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't turn a blind eye when I saw them trying to mug him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.35,0:11:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told myself I just had to protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty stupid, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was really brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the least I could do for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I wanna find my self-worth in something beyond simply being there for Yukiko,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm always pushing myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,telling myself I gotta get stronger and try even harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satonaka, you're already working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I count on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want you to push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I got a text!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said, "Rise's taking everyone out to a club."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. So this is a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh shoot, I'm getting pumped up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:12:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, I never expected to run into you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it permitted for high school students such as yourselves to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought you here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a reputable club, so I was checking it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as if I was otherwise preoccupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's hang out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together? You're inviting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you eat with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you aren't busy, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been really eager to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious how someone my age is working as a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, if you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? You look a little red.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get us the VIP room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, a VIP room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know some people. Just give me a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko, how many have you had?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure this is all right? Isn't it expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I held a secret show here, the power went out in the middle of it, and the gig was canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is on the house today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! You serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.66,0:14:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I won't hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! We won't hold back either! Right, Kanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanji, drink up and start singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanji, you're so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanji... Kanji. Kanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Kanjecture that something's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanjecture?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanjecture!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}There are good and bad Kanjectures.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko's a bit looser than usual, too.{that's how i like it}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great Kanjecture!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't tell me this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:15:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told 'em to give us soft drinks! They're non-alcoholic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, I was wondering why it's so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told them! I really did!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these seriously alcoholic... drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kings Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare the sticks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King's orders are absolute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your butt in gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-When did he get those?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King's orders are absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da! Everyone, take your pick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So who's the King?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teddie's is red! Teddie's the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this can't end well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As King, I order number three to give me a smooch...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without delay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kissy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude! Not number three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about number two?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it! No take-backs, Kingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smooch! Yay, smooch! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A-A smooch?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanji, I knew you had your eyes set on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll give you my innocence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, don't! I'll freakin' kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the first round, and two contestants have dropped out already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that kind of game?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On to round two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the King?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:17:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No crazy orders this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how it goes! If the last King demanded a smooch,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then the next order's gotta be more extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should rest on his lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make 'em sit on his lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skip straight to hugging!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Piggybacks are all the rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on. Make up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit on my lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King's order is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...absolute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me next!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chie, you gotta hug him like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, lowly commoners! That King's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu, don't hog all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I'm the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me next! I'm the King! Actually, the Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't even draw a chopstick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have someone talk about something really embarrassing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that they'd never wanna tell anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up, Naoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to if you don't want to, Naoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in exchange, you all have to tell me about something as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of any embarrassing stories, so I'll explain my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shirogane family line has been helping the police as detectives for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the fifth generation with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm living with my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the {\i1}Kindaichi Case Files!{TL Note: Kindaichi Case Files is a Japanese anime, manga and light novel series about a high school  detective named Kousuke Kindaichi. His grandfather was once a famous detective.TL Note: Nobody cares.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandfather has deep connections with the police
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks after me, despite my youth and inexperience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?! No punchline?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Sorry for the letdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoto, that's so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fill her up, on the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you seriously drunk, dude?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to hear your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:20:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A straight answer, please. What is your true involvement with the murder case?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you're so good at killing the mood that it's almost funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we go rescuing people who've been kidnapped by jumping into the TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, we use our Personas to beat up Shadows...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mocking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Issh true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Persona! Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sheesh, somebody put these two drunks to bed already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see now that you had no intention of telling me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But really, this isn't alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I confirmed it when I first entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No alcohol has been served here since a rash of drunk driving last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Does that mean we're drunk off the atmosphere?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:21:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to get back with three of them out cold? Right, Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fill her up, straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.59,0:21:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a group of imbeciles?
