Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:13.79,Shop Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(521,337)\frz8.169\fax-0.2\blur1\fry5\c&HE0DCD8&}GA
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:13.79,Shop Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(697,301)\blur1\fax-0.2\c&HE0DCD8&\frz13.557\fry-10}K{\fry0}U
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:13.79,Shop Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(909,262)\blur1\fax-0.15\frz9.316\c&HE0DCD8&}R{\frx10}E
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang! This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here a lot when we were shooting dramas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've got the best ramen in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what happened last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I think the two us fell asleep quick. I heard it got pretty wild, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.41,0:21:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took things a little too seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My head is killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing working here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An acquaintance runs the shop, so I'm training here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You even train during trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this the Hagakure Bow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know it was on the regular menu now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.11,0:21:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up before it gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.52,0:21:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can eat it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be a pal and help out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.95,0:22:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was still eating that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.72,0:22:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you were all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.66,0:22:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was not!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.50,0:22:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just about time for us to head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that late already?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.40,0:22:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking back, I had a pretty good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we get Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's pick it out together!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.98,0:22:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All righty, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.08,0:22:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so stuffed I can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.46,0:22:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen's orders are absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Teddie. I'm leaving you here along with the memories of my youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.65,0:22:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Help me! I can't cover my ticket back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.81,0:24:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Regarding those materials...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.47,0:24:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take them. Send them over ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.55,0:24:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.57,0:24:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up and gather information on Naoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.72,0:24:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.48,0:24:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think of this as a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.20,0:24:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.64,0:24:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.76,0:22:53.05,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I look at the rustic scenery
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.05,0:22:55.77,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}along the path to school
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:23:01.52,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}we walked together {kimi to aruita tsuugakuro hinabiru keshiki mitsumete}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:07.03,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Campus in spring,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:10.41,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}the summer festival {haru no koutei kasenshiki natsu matsuri}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:14.66,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}These were the days we spent
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:17.66,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}shoulder-to-shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.66,0:23:22.46,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}laughing together {minna de waratte katayose sugoshiteta hibi}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:30.02,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}From past to present {kono ninake nai nichijou wo nagamete}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:34.18,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I've always
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:36.60,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}looked back on these
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:39.64,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}carefree days {kako kara ima made sugoshite kita yo}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.90,0:23:47.53,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}From today to tomorrow {kyou kara asu ashita kara mirai he}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.24,0:24:00.00,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\t(\b0\c&H303030&\3c&HFFFFFF&)}We move forward while treasuring the bonds we've made {minna to kizuita kizuna himete aruki dasu}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.48,0:24:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for the body-altering operation!
